*kconvert-1.1-r1 (24 Feb 2005)

  24 Feb 2005; Marcus D. Hanwell <cryos@gentoo.org>
  +files/kconvert-1.1-arts-configure.patch, +kconvert-1.1-r1.ebuild,
  kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  Fixed up the ebuild to use kde.eclass, added a configure patch to build
  without arts and changed to need-kde 3. This fixes bug 82095. Also updated the
  description a little.

*kconvert-1.1 (24 Dec 2004)

  24 Dec 2004; Olivier Fisette <ribosome@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  Moved from app-sci/kconvert to sci-calculators/kconvert.

  03 Sep 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  01 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  virtual/glibc -> virtual/libc

  29 May 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  Fixed sandbox violation and marked ~amd64.

  19 Apr 2004; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org> kconvert-1.1.ebuild:
  Adding IUSE

